formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project  solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing.Land cost is taken at actuals without indexing.basis the land document and related supporting documents provided to us.As informed to us there is no material in work in progress.We have relied upon  information provided by the management for  the numbers and areas given for covered and open parking and garages  as we are not technical person to certify the same. The same is the case with Carpet Area, Balcony Area and Terrace Area as mentioned in the certificate. The balcony area   include wash area. The Promoter has made certain expenditure from his central bank account for which the details are yet not provided by him , hence only expenditure pertaining to Land expenditure is taken from his central bank account. Moreover though Designated RERA Bank A/c No is 10050720990 ,however RERA utilisation  A/c is updated as 10050720978 RA3 and RA4. there are some inventory in which excess amount is received compared to the banakhat amount , we have shown received amount upto the value of unit consideration mentioned in Banakhat. Promoter's existing rera account has been closed by the bank on 1/5/2021, promoter has to apply for BCR before filing the next quarterly progress report. since the RERA Bank account is changed by the promoter but not updated here on the portal we have given closing bank balance of the exisiting account only. promoter has opened new RERA Acc with the same bank as per RERA Guidelines and closing Balance of that account is Rs 31977.32/-

physProgressList.reason: As informed to us by the promoter,he is yet to book/obtain invoices for the construction
